  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2739420/extras/9e095abdb21a2f34993f452b1cb590cd.avif?t=1746060096\" width=616 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2739420/extras/eae9bd6bdf6e5f96667499059aee6585.webp?t=1746060096\" width=500 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >刚上大一，魏明诚就喜欢上了系花江雪。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >到大二时，他终于按捺不住这份心情，对江雪表白了。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >他被拒绝了。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >正在魏明诚伤心失落之际，在他面前突然出现一位打扮奇特又可爱的女生，自称是仙子，要教魏明诚怎么追女生。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >仙子说，“需要经过系统的学习，经历严酷的磨练，制定周全的计划，才能最终实现你的理想！” </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >魏明诚立刻决定接受仙子的帮助。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >第二天，第一节课就要开始了。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一个甜蜜，青涩，酸苦的校园恋爱故事。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >发生在桃花漫舞的，忧郁的，犹豫的春季。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这场从心碎开始的旅途，会走向怎样的结局呢？ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2739420/extras/12cf2615204503e2f30515ee6627f9ac.webp?t=1746060096\" width=500 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2739420/extras/cac0164dcea7772819beb3745805939f.avif?t=1746060096\" width=616 height=3000 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2739420/extras/c7702e325d818b77fe57c3c86152621d.webp?t=1746060096\" width=500 height=50 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >22万字的扎实剧本。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >相比上一部作品，故事节奏大幅优化，从光速降低为超音速，依旧十分紧凑，无日常无尿点。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >没有魔法，扎根于现实的恋爱故事。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩《书恋与君》，品现充人生。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2739420/extras/97f589b412832f59e4181923aa0d5d04.webp?t=1746060096\" width=500 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Q群：167222263 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >微博：@磷光工作室的沙哥</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >b站：@磷光工作室的沙哥</p>",
